snippet.title: W.T. promotion video
snippet.description:
一人称視点脱出ゲーム「W.T.」のプロモーション動画です。
2023年 Steamにて発売予定
(画面は開発中のものにつき、製品版では異なる点があるかもしれません）

This is a promotion video for the first-person escape game "W.T."
Scheduled for release on Steam in 2023.
(The screen may differ from the final product as it is still under development)

Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2426100/WT/
